Sixshot/Ares:




Sixshot fired off two blasts from his weapon several inches away from 
Rainchark's head.  "Good, follow us."

"And don't try anything!" Ares yelled, glaring.  He was about to say 
something else, but he and Sixshot received the transmissions from the IGL.

"Where the slag is Shockwave and Unitron?  We need to talk to them..." Ares 
said to himself as both Neo 'Cons headed for the nearest entry way of the 
Ramora, motioning for Rainchark to follow.
